Package jetbrains.mps.ide.editorTabs.tabfactory.emptytabs

Class EmptyTabsComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • jetbrains.mps.ide.editorTabs.tabfactory.emptytabs.EmptyTabsComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TabsComponent
    public class EmptyTabsComponent
extends Object
implements TabsComponent
    Class for 'Do not show tabs' option in Editor 'Aspect tabs' setting. Only store SNodeReference to current editing node and calls myCallback.changeNode() when it changed. Does not have own JComponent. It just delegate everything.
